sentence: Mahagama Sekera (Mahagamage Sekara) (Sinhala:මහගම සේකර / මහගමගේ සේකර ) (7 April 1929 – 14 January 1976)
Sri Lankan poet, lyricist, playwright, novelist, artist, translator and filmmaker.
